# Content SEO (.antigravityrules)

- E-E-A-T: org JSON-LD in root layout; article authors/dates; HTTPS + headers
- CWV targets: LCP ≤2.5s · INP ≤200ms · CLS ≤0.1 — tactics in `10-mobile` / `11-desktop` rules
- Schema via `components/seo/*` + `pageMetadata()` — match visible title/description
- One H1; Urdu `alt`; internal links between pillars/clusters
- No keyword stuffing, dark patterns, or misleading metadata
- `llms.txt` + AI bots in `robots.ts` (English OK for llms)

